      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still photograph shows a man (Emin Belig Belli) and a woman (Anna Mariyeviҫ) on a hill. At the foot of the hill are houses and an area of water with ships and boats on it.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature ‘Istanbul'da bir facia-i aşk’ (A love tragedy in Istanbul) was directed by Muhsin Ertuğrul and released in 1922. The water in the picture is obviously the Bosphorus.</ab>
